entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You intercepted the transports and destroyed them, along with their three escaping droids.
entries.journal_entry_description: The last piece of the droid is its head and EV-9D9 has it. Problem is EV-9D9 is considerably distracted by her own problems. So she wants you to help her out first. First she needs three droids tracked down and destroyed.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You need to get to a space terminal in order to do this mission for EV-9D9. The nearest one is outside Jabba's Palace.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to EV-9D9 when you have destroyed the droids transports.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: EV-9D9 has three runaway droids that are trying to escape Tatooine. You have the task of destroying the transports that are carrying her wayward droids.
